    public class WordRedGreenOutfilter
extends WordBufferingFilter
    This class is used to sort sequences of added/deleted words. Given a mixed sequence of consecutive added and deleted words (including spaces and punctuation), this filter will sort them so that all the deleted words and added words appear together.
